/**
 * @page mastering_utility_tests Mastering Utility Tests
 *
 * @brief Overview of the main test suite for the Mastering Utility project.
 *
 * This page describes the testing components responsible for validating
 * metadata handling and file persistence.
 *
 * @section features Key Features
 *
 * @subsection data_gen Test Data Generation
 * Creates MasteringUtility::Album and MasteringUtility::Song instances filled
 * with example metadata for use in the tests.
 *
 * @subsection markup_persist Markup Persistence Test
 * The test suite:
 * - Uses MasteringUtility::SaveMarkup to write album and song metadata to a
 *   temporary `.mas` file.
 * - Uses MasteringUtility::ParseMarkup to load the metadata back from the file.
 *
 * @subsection validation Data Validation
 * Compares each field of the original data structures against the parsed ones
 * to ensure proper serialization and deserialization behavior.
 *
 * @subsection perf Performance Measurement
 * Measures the execution time of the tests to keep track of performance
 * characteristics.
 */
